# VHS tape for the README demo GIF — https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Regenerate with: vhs demo/demo.tape
Output demo/demo.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "npx qufox-docs serve ./notes"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "# edit a note in your editor — the browser reloads on save"
Sleep 2s
